All Classes

Class Summary
Class Description
Columns
The Columns class generates tables by evenly spacing passed strings in a row format.
Expense
Expense class is a clone of the Transaction class, but serves as "Type Security" The class is used to classify all Transactions of type Expense.
Income
Income class is a clone of the Transaction class, but serves as "Type Security" The class is used to classify all Transactions of type Income.
Main
This class serves as an entry point to the tracker app and nothing else.
Storage
Storage contains static methods used to save and restore Tracker objects which form the core of the FinTrack app.
Tracker
The Tracker class is designed to store Transaction objects.
TrackerApp
TrackerApp is main class is the sense that it is responsible for the for all method calls, Ui navigation and general implementation of all the features available in other classes.
Transaction
Abstract class to serve as a base for transaction type objects.
UiInput
UiInput is designed to take console input of type LocalDate, double, int or String.
UiText
